  "title": "Driver",
  "description": "<p><strong>Description</strong></p><p><strong>The Job:</strong></p><p>1. Support daily distribution operation requirements</p><p>2. Ensure correct loading of goods onto delivery vehicles</p><p>3. Ensure timely delivery of goods to customer</p><p>4. Assist to unload and organize goods at customer premise in a safe manner</p><p>5. Provide excellent customer service during delivery</p><p>6. Adhere to assigned routes and follow time schedules</p><p>7. Abid by all transportation laws and maintain safe driving records</p><p>8. Handle vehicles, equipment and devices provided by company with care</p><p>9. Maintain basic housekeeping, cleanliness and hygiene of vehicle assigned</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>1. Candidates need to possess Class 3 Licence</p><p>2. Good communication skills</p><p>3. Able to commit to 5.5 day work week schedule</p><p>4. Have basic knowledge in preventive maintenance of vehicle</p>",
